  "original_title": "Fuel distribution to 12 filling stations suspended: Minister",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel distribution to 12 filling stations suspended: Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The power and energy ministry today decided to suspend fuel distribution to 12 filling stations that did not comply with the fuel dispensing guidelines, Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said.",
        "He said the decision was taken following the progress review of the CPC Marketing division held today.",
        "During the meeting, it was reviewed about the failure to comply with QR system by certain fuel stations.",
        "However, the Minister has given instructions to continuously monitor the stations and to submit complaints received by the public to the respective police stations. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
